{"tid":2046744,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要團結香港人，首先要打倒「港人治港」呢個最大分化scheme！","createTime":"2020-06-01T15:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T15:52:16.000Z","uid":76712,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05776555ea9f6697e07656fdd984e0d60d096aae","tid":2046744,"uid":76712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:12:21.000Z","msg":"既然一國一制已成現實<br />\n點解仲需要呢班香港高官做北京嘅代理人管治香港？<br />\nat this point佢地嘅存在已經可有可無！<br />\n<br />\n與其日日睇住港共班廢官，同埋民建聯工聯會呢班低學歷垃圾係度呃飯食<br />\n我寧願中聯辦港澳辦個班北佬走上台前直接取締港共<br />\n香港唔再需要特首，只需要市委書記<br />\n<br />\n與其睇住班毅進黑警收錢ot打香港人<br />\n我寧願出手嘅係中國公安，係中國武警<br />\n我想睇到嘅，係中國公安全面取締黑警<br />\n香港黑警全面失業<br />\n<br />\n我地要打倒呢班既得利益者<br />\n我地要佢地一齊接受京人治港<br />\n要佢地深切體會被殖民究竟係咩感覺<br />\n要佢地一齊感受主流香港人面對緊嘅苦<br />\n繼而令佢地萌生保家衛國嘅本土主義嘅思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人要成為真正團結強大嘅民族<br />\n就首先要不分黃藍，團結大多數香港人<br />\n要團結，有咩方法好過一齊共患難呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊共患難，到時候不論黃藍，大家目標都會一致<br />\n就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊以推翻殖民政府，民族自決，香港獨立建國為目標！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以一句講曬，「港人治港」根本係最大嘅分化scheme黎！我地要打倒「港人治港」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bfa9bbaa8a30c387bd73871b183c929a00521f2","tid":2046744,"uid":76712,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:14:48.000Z","msg":"If you burn, you burn with us<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcb0b365ef9c047a8f1bebbf0acc88f4f22dd53","tid":2046744,"uid":76712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6bfa9bbaa8a30c387bd73871b183c929a00521f2","tid":2046744,"uid":76712,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:14:48.000Z","msg":"If you burn, you burn with us<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"We<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a115eba4da6f88cade645a4e43ecb592b0573c78","tid":2046744,"uid":76712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:26:16.000Z","msg":"No one gives a fuck<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384ab6fc5857c282fc81eed1927ea6c10e6cc37c","tid":2046744,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"咁如果中共掠奪你嘅資源 分俾藍絲<br />\n係咪解決咗個問題？"},{"pid":"879f77483e1dba7aa2ea8067f43f9c4b6a8d95fd","tid":2046744,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"正如廣東省武警幾千蚊同香港POPO 2皮幾一樣"},{"pid":"9bdb25df5fcc88114d3cbef1a2a5dfd7cf4ccbc5","tid":2046744,"uid":103521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:40:40.000Z","msg":"道理都合理，但你要一個更強既campaign口號先得"},{"pid":"51a5bed016438ab1ff87e00427355458028eb0ad","tid":2046744,"uid":108993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"384ab6fc5857c282fc81eed1927ea6c10e6cc37c","tid":2046744,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"咁如果中共掠奪你嘅資源 分俾藍絲<br />\n係咪解決咗個問題？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"符合中国既統戰策略<br />\n拉攏次要敵打擊主要敵人"},{"pid":"035968c24fb1757bf9f99d0f00ab5860b612e48c","tid":2046744,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"879f77483e1dba7aa2ea8067f43f9c4b6a8d95fd","tid":2046744,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"正如廣東省武警幾千蚊同香港POPO 2皮幾一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T15:52:16.000Z","msg":"佢安個「中國香港特警」名俾黑警咪得囉"}]}